---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base";
import SocialList from "@/components/SocialList";
---

<PageLayout meta={{ title: "Portfolio" }}>
	<section>
		<h1 class="title mb-6">Professional Portfolio</h1>
		<p class="mb-4">
			I'm a full-stack developer and carpenter working at <strong>Uresco Construction Materials</strong>. My expertise combines web development, software engineering, and hands-on construction knowledge to solve real-world problems in the lumber and materials industry.
		</p>
		<SocialList />
	</section>

	<div class="section-grid">
		<section class="mt-16">
			<h2 class="title mb-4 text-xl">Areas of Expertise</h2>
			<ul class="space-y-4">
				<li>
					<strong>Web Development</strong>
					<p class="mt-2">Full-stack development with JavaScript/TypeScript, React, Astro, and Node.js. Building responsive, performant web applications and interfaces.</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Warehouse Management Systems</strong>
					<p class="mt-2">Database design, inventory tracking, material management systems, and supply chain optimization for the lumber industry.</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>3D Visualization & WebGL</strong>
					<p class="mt-2">Creating interactive 3D visualization tools for construction materials, spatial planning, and material visualization using Three.js and WebGL.</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Geolocation & Logistics</strong>
					<p class="mt-2">GPS tracking, mapping integrations, location-based services, and real-time logistics applications for field operations and material delivery.</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Carpentry & Construction</strong>
					<p class="mt-2">Hands-on experience with lumber, building materials, and practical construction knowledge that informs software solutions.</p>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section class="mt-16">
			<h2 class="title mb-4 text-xl">Technical Skills</h2>
			<ul class="space-y-4">
				<li>
					<strong>Languages:</strong> JavaScript, TypeScript, Python, SQL
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Frontend:</strong> React, Astro, Tailwind CSS, Framer Motion, Responsive Design
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Backend:</strong> Node.js, Express, Database Design & Optimization
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>3D/Graphics:</strong> Three.js, WebGL, Canvas, Spatial Visualization
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Geolocation:</strong> Mapping APIs, GPS Integration, Real-time Tracking
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Tools & Platforms:</strong> Git, Docker, REST APIs, GraphQL
				</li>
			</ul>
		</section>
	</div>

	<section class="mt-16">
		<h2 class="title mb-4 text-xl">Technologies & Frameworks</h2>
		<ul class="space-y-4 sm:space-y-2">
			<li>
				<a
					href="https://astro.build"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noopener noreferrer"
					class="cactus-link inline-block"
				>Astro</a>:
				<p class="inline-block sm:mt-2">Build fast websites, faster. Perfect for building performant static and hybrid sites.</p>
			</li>
			<li>
				<a
					href="https://react.dev"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noopener noreferrer"
					class="cactus-link inline-block"
				>React</a>:
				<p class="inline-block sm:mt-2">A JavaScript library for building interactive user interfaces with component-based architecture.</p>
			</li>
			<li>
				<a
					href="https://threejs.org"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noopener noreferrer"
					class="cactus-link inline-block"
				>Three.js</a>:
				<p class="inline-block sm:mt-2">JavaScript 3D library for creating interactive 3D visualizations and spatial applications.</p>
			</li>
			<li>
				<a
					href="https://tailwindcss.com"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noopener noreferrer"
					class="cactus-link inline-block"
				>Tailwind CSS</a>:
				<p class="inline-block sm:mt-2">Utility-first CSS framework for rapidly building modern, responsive designs.</p>
			</li>
			<li>
				<a
					href="https://www.postgresql.org/"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noopener noreferrer"
					class="cactus-link inline-block"
				>PostgreSQL</a>:
				<p class="inline-block sm:mt-2">Powerful, open-source relational database for building scalable applications and inventory systems.</p>
			</li>
			<li>
				<a
					href="https://nodejs.org"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noopener noreferrer"
					class="cactus-link inline-block"
				>Node.js</a>:
				<p class="inline-block sm:mt-2">JavaScript runtime for building scalable server-side applications and APIs.</p>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</section>

	<section class="mt-16">
		<h2 class="title mb-4 text-xl">Get In Touch</h2>
		<p class="mb-4">
			Interested in collaborating or learning more about my work? Feel free to reach out through any of my social channels or email me at <a class="hover:underline" href="mailto:matthieufelker@skiff.com">matthieufelker@skiff.com</a>.
		</p>
	</section>
</PageLayout>
